    <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
    <p>
     GOOD-FRIEND
     <br/>
     Link your index fingers to show a bond. Pull it forward twice to show the bond 
is not easily broken.
     <br/>
     <img border="0" height="223" src="../../signjpegs/f/friend-good1.jpg" width="218"/>
